{"tid":338578,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又係你]薛國強城規會申請解放軍總部改劃商業用地 搬至槍會山昂船洲軍營","createTime":"2017-07-28T09:55:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T16:17:02.000Z","uid":26506,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b9ec74fc3f64d534d9c48af9d111058fa7c2b213","tid":338578,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T09:55:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1344919-20170728.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1344919-20170728.htm&d=WB9wSc5z1ZO9upoRyOJmuYsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=a2739720\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1344919-20170728.htm&h=4baf0287\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1344919-20170728.htm</a><br />\n城規會討論將軍事用地改為商業用地的建議<br />\n2017-07-28 HKT 12:28<br />\n兩度提出將中環駐港解放軍總部，改劃為酒店用途但被城規會否決的規劃師薛國強，早前再向城規會呈交申請，建議將軍事用地改為商業用地，城規會早上開會討論。<br />\n<br />\n薛國強在申請書中建議，可將解放軍總部用地整合至槍會山軍營和昂船洲軍營，而原本的中環用地則改作商業用地最為適合。<br />\n<br />\n規劃署表明反對，指有關用地一直用作駐軍總部，受法例保護供香港駐軍作防禦之用；保安局和發展局亦表明改劃用地不恰當。規劃署指申請人沒有提供任何參考數據和評估報告，未能討論改劃後所帶來的好處和壞處。若批准申請會立下不良先例，影響軍事防禦目的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E8%A6%8F%E5%8A%83%E7%BD%B2%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E5%9F%8E%E8%A6%8F%E6%9C%83%E5%B0%87%E4%B8%AD%E7%92%B0%E9%A7%90%E6%B8%AF%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D%E7%B8%BD%E9%83%A8%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%94%B9%E5%8A%83%E7%82%BA%E5%95%86%E7%94%A8-88984\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E8%25A6%258F%25E5%258A%2583%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E5%259F%258E%25E8%25A6%258F%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25B0%2587%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%2592%25B0%25E9%25A7%2590%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%2594%25BE%25E8%25BB%258D%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E9%2583%25A8%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%258A%2583%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%2595%2586%25E7%2594%25A8-88984&d=WB9wSc5z1ZO9upoRyOJmuYsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=b6437590\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E8%A6%8F%E5%8A%83%E7%BD%B2%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E5%9F%8E%E8%A6%8F%E6%9C%83%E5%B0%87%E4%B8%AD%E7%92%B0%E9%A7%90%E6%B8%AF%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D%E7%B8%BD%E9%83%A8%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%94%B9%E5%8A%83%E7%82%BA%E5%95%86%E7%94%A8-88984</a><br />\n規劃署反對城規會將中環駐港解放軍總部用地改劃為商用<br />\n3 小時前<br />\n城規會審議將中環駐港解放軍總部用地，改劃為商業用途的申請。規劃署表明反對，署方指，申請地點已宣布為軍事設施禁區及受保護地方，供香港駐軍防禦之用，如果批准改劃，會為其他同類申請立下不良先例，影響軍事用地的防禦目的。加上申請人薛國強沒有提供任何發展參數及建議等支持意見，署方質疑更改規劃會否對鄰近地區有負面影響。<br />\n<br />\n薛國強在會上表示，申請改劃用途可以配合國家日後發展一帶一路<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n585th Metro Planning Committee meeting (28 Jul 2017)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/tpb/en/whats_new/Agenda/585_mpc-Agenda-I.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Ftpb%2Fen%2Fwhats_new%2FAgenda%2F585_mpc-Agenda-I.pdf&d=WB9wSc5z1ZO9upoRyOJmuYsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=4a5fa820\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.info.gov.hk/tpb/en/whats_new/Agenda/585_mpc-Agenda-I.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\nY/H24/8 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/tpb/en/plan_application/Y_H24_8.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Ftpb%2Fen%2Fplan_application%2FY_H24_8.html&d=WB9wSc5z1ZO9upoRyOJmuYsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=b1011ae6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.info.gov.hk/tpb/en/plan_application/Y_H24_8.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/tpb/en/plan_application/Attachment/20170512/s12a_eng_news.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Ftpb%2Fen%2Fplan_application%2FAttachment%2F20170512%2Fs12a_eng_news.pdf&d=WB9wSc5z1ZO9upoRyOJmuYsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=61fef77d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.info.gov.hk/tpb/en/plan_application/Attachment/20170512/s12a_eng_news.pdf</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/tpb/tc/plan_application/Attachment/20170512/s12a_Y_H24_8_0_gist.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/l